---
title: Honey Soy & Sesame Chicken Strips with Radish & Peanut Slaw Quick Prep | Ready in 15 | Serves 2
description: Tender honey soy glazed chicken strips, creamy radish slaw and crispy shallots all in one – we promise, this combo
is love at first bite! And second bite, and third bite... Pack it up and enjoy it for a lunch that'll be the envy of all.
